---
title: Taco-Style Beef Bowl with Basmati Rice and Lime Crema
description: Easy, fast and packed with flavour, this dish gives you the fiesta without the fuss! Bell peppers and green onions pair perfectly with tender beef for a fun taco bowl that comes together with our fabulous Mexican seasoning.
